OL,12,     GThe Joshua Tree: Bono, The Edge,
OL,13,     GAdam Clayton, Larry Mullen and
OL,14,     Gproducers Brian Eno and Daniel
OL,15,     GLanois give an insight into the
OL,16,     Gmaking of their 1987 smash The
OL,17,     GJoshua Tree.
